author: Tyler Sipe
title: UW takes on 10th ranked Stanford
text: UW takes on 10th ranked Stanford   7:42 pm K.J. Carta-Samuels warms up as quarterback for Washington Saturday night at Stanford. Washington played Stanford Saturday, October 24, 2015 at Stanford Stadium in Palo Alto, Calif. (Dean Rutz / The Seattle Times) Jake Browning watches while his backups warm up Saturday at Stanford. It was not immediately known if the injured Browning would start for the Huskies. (Dean Rutz / The Seattle Times) Washington coach Chris Petersen walks the turf at Stanford Stadium before Saturday’s game. (Dean Rutz / The Seattle Times) K.J.
